	    and add a unit-test.
	* meta.c: call meta_init() before makefiles are read and if built
	  with filemon support set .MAKE.PATH_FILEMON to _PATH_FILEMON
	  this let's makefiles test for support.
	  Call meta_mode_init() to process .MAKE.MODE.

